<h2 id="process">Process</h2>

<div class="image-container"><img src="../img/watson/siteaudit.png" alt="Original Site Audit" /></div>

<p>One of the first steps we took was looking at the current state of affairs of the site. The pages were divided into 3 main groups: about, current festival and past festivals. The current festival and past festival sections were very much the same minus a schedule of events. Both sections housed their respective artist pages displaying the work they presented.</p>

